structure.unit: PHYSICIANS, OSTEOPATHS, PODIATRISTS, AND RELATED MEDICAL PRACTITIONERS

law.text: Any person who intentionally or recklessly violates KRS 311.715 shall be guilty of a Class A misdemeanor.
law.history: Amended 2010 Ky. Acts ch. 161, sec. 35, effective July 15, 2010. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 19, sec. 5(4), (5), effective July 15, 1986. -- Created 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 377, sec. 10, effective July 13, 1984.
